349
00:19:12.210 --> 00:19:16.050
You had us in tears as vee desperately
tried to figure out the reason vhyy.

350
00:19:16.800 --> 00:19:18.890
Our faith in you vass tested!

351
00:19:26.270 --> 00:19:28.610
Over one month ago,

352
00:19:29.360 --> 00:19:35.240
during the Reverie, the World Conference
held in the Holy Land, Mary Geoise...

353
00:19:38.700 --> 00:19:42.370
This is an emergency! Intruders have
invaded the Land of the Gods!

354
00:19:42.700 --> 00:19:44.870
Please evacuate immediately!

355
00:19:44.870 --> 00:19:47.830
Our food reserves were blown up!

356
00:19:47.830 --> 00:19:51.840
Do something, you bureaucrats!
Get rid of these intruders!

357
00:19:51.840 --> 00:19:56.550
Four Revolutionary Army commanders
have been identified on the premises!

358
00:19:56.550 --> 00:19:58.550
Damn it all!

359
00:19:58.550 --> 00:20:01.680
Not only do they destroy
the very symbol of the World Nobles,

360
00:20:01.680 --> 00:20:04.310
but they even target
our gourmet food reserves!

361
00:20:04.310 --> 00:20:06.940
The jealousy of the poor knows no bounds!

362
00:20:06.940 --> 00:20:09.270
Capture them and remove their heads at once!

363
00:20:09.730 --> 00:20:12.980
You guards are next on the chopping block!

364
00:20:13.360 --> 00:20:17.450
Did you think you could just let this
happen to us and get away with it?!

365
00:20:21.870 --> 00:20:26.080
I told you to get a move on! Worthless mutt!

366
00:20:29.790 --> 00:20:32.670
Imagine if something were to happen to me!

367
00:20:32.670 --> 00:20:34.250
Go faster!

368
00:20:43.100 --> 00:20:44.430
Ouch!

369
00:20:45.640 --> 00:20:48.190
You useless bastard!

370
00:20:48.190 --> 00:20:51.020
Forget it! I'll just walk on my own!

371
00:20:53.060 --> 00:20:55.070
You're fired.

372
00:20:56.570 --> 00:20:58.070
You piece of trash!

373
00:21:06.870 --> 00:21:08.080
My gun!

374
00:21:09.330 --> 00:21:11.540
Who did that?!

375
00:21:12.040 --> 00:21:14.380
What gives you the right...

376
00:21:14.380 --> 00:21:16.840
to treat other people like scum?!

377
00:21:17.170 --> 00:21:18.760
Karasoot!

378
00:21:24.180 --> 00:21:25.970
Head to the east side of town.

379
00:21:25.970 --> 00:21:26.930
What?

380
00:21:27.270 --> 00:21:29.020
O-Okay!

381
00:21:29.940 --> 00:21:32.900
Saint Pluming! Please evacuate quickly!

382
00:21:32.900 --> 00:21:35.860
Cipher Pol... what took you so long?!

383
00:21:35.860 --> 00:21:38.940
Eliminate that vermin at once!

384
00:21:38.940 --> 00:21:40.570
The Revolutionary Army?!

385
00:21:40.570 --> 00:21:41.950
Open fire!

386
00:21:48.080 --> 00:21:50.330
Nice, we got him!

387
00:21:50.330 --> 00:21:51.830
Fill him with lead!

388
00:21:51.830 --> 00:21:54.790
Turn him to dust!

389
00:21:57.000 --> 00:21:58.000
What?!

390
00:21:58.000 --> 00:22:01.680
H-He actually turned to dust...

391
00:22:01.680 --> 00:22:03.800
What is he...?

392
00:22:03.800 --> 00:22:05.140
Did we get him?

393
00:22:12.480 --> 00:22:14.150
Obelisoots!

394
00:22:32.290 --> 00:22:33.670
You piece of trash.

395
00:22:34.210 --> 00:22:36.880
<b>Commander Karasu
(Soot-Soot Fruit)
Northern Forces
Revolutionary Army</b>

396
00:22:45.720 --> 00:22:47.350
Help me already!

397
00:22:47.350 --> 00:22:48.680
Save me!

398
00:22:51.640 --> 00:22:54.390
Masters! I'm begging you!

399
00:22:54.770 --> 00:22:57.060
Please let us escape, too!

400
00:22:57.060 --> 00:22:59.520
Help us!

401
00:22:59.520 --> 00:23:01.400
There they are!

402
00:23:04.110 --> 00:23:06.700
I'm here to save you all!

403
00:23:10.950 --> 00:23:12.080
Everyone...

404
00:23:12.080 --> 00:23:13.660
stay right where you are!

405
00:23:14.620 --> 00:23:17.790
Laser Shooter!

406
00:23:28.550 --> 00:23:29.850
Hurry up!

407
00:23:29.850 --> 00:23:31.970
Wait at the east side of town!

408
00:23:31.970 --> 00:23:33.980
We're all getting out of here together!

409
00:23:35.480 --> 00:23:37.730
Th-Thank you!

410
00:23:37.730 --> 00:23:40.570
– Thank you!
– Thank you!

411
00:23:40.570 --> 00:23:42.230
You can thank me later!

412
00:23:42.570 --> 00:23:44.400
Make sure you get there!

413
00:23:48.070 --> 00:23:50.740
Would you look at that!

414
00:23:51.410 --> 00:23:54.040
<b>Commander Lindbergh
Southern Forces
Revolutionary Army</b>

415
00:23:54.500 --> 00:23:57.000
Lindbergh! Enemies are headed this way!

416
00:23:57.420 --> 00:23:58.120
Huh?

417
00:23:58.500 --> 00:24:00.750
Hurry up and finish freeing the slaves!

418
00:24:00.750 --> 00:24:01.880
Got it!

419
00:24:05.380 --> 00:24:07.760
Something is coming...

420
00:24:07.760 --> 00:24:09.340
Something strong!

421
00:24:14.140 --> 00:24:15.350
Crow...

422
00:24:18.310 --> 00:24:19.900
Soul Lotus!

423
00:24:49.090 --> 00:24:50.590
Get back here!

424
00:24:50.590 --> 00:24:53.890
Lowly slaves have no right to defy me!

425
00:24:55.430 --> 00:24:55.930
Huh?

426
00:25:04.020 --> 00:25:05.360
What's going on?!

427
00:25:05.360 --> 00:25:08.320
Oh, my bad.

428
00:25:08.320 --> 00:25:09.950
A giant?!

429
00:25:13.780 --> 00:25:15.910
That's not nice!

430
00:25:15.910 --> 00:25:19.620
You have to stop shooting people like that!

431
00:25:19.620 --> 00:25:22.540
Hey guys, you gotta get outta here!

432
00:25:22.540 --> 00:25:24.290
Get to the east side of town!

433
00:25:24.290 --> 00:25:26.800
My friends are expecting you!

434
00:25:27.460 --> 00:25:30.130
<b>Commander Morley
Western Forces
Revolutionary Army</b>

435
00:25:30.470 --> 00:25:32.640
And make sure to be careful!

436
00:25:32.640 --> 00:25:34.220
Thank you!

437
00:25:38.310 --> 00:25:42.060
You damn Revolutionary Army punks!

438
00:25:48.190 --> 00:25:51.570
I'm sure you understand...

439
00:25:51.570 --> 00:25:55.240
what it means to oppose
the Celestial Dragons!

440
00:25:59.290 --> 00:26:00.160
Ew!

441
00:26:06.090 --> 00:26:08.550
What's wrong with this boy?!

442
00:26:08.550 --> 00:26:10.760
Someone has anger issues!

443
00:26:11.130 --> 00:26:12.510
It's because you punks...

444
00:26:13.010 --> 00:26:15.140
are destroying the damn town!

445
00:26:15.140 --> 00:26:17.260
Where did your leader go?!

446
00:26:17.260 --> 00:26:20.520
Why are you asking
me questions, naughty boy?!

447
00:26:20.520 --> 00:26:21.980
What a pervert!

448
00:26:21.980 --> 00:26:23.100
Huh?!

449
00:26:23.100 --> 00:26:25.230
That's rich, coming from you!

450
00:26:25.230 --> 00:26:26.940
Look what you're wearing!

451
00:26:28.900 --> 00:26:31.360
Hey, my eyes are up here!

452
00:26:33.110 --> 00:26:34.610
Whoa...

453
00:26:34.610 --> 00:26:36.830
Why are you staring at me?

454
00:26:37.370 --> 00:26:39.120
Do you...

455
00:26:39.120 --> 00:26:40.450
like me?!

456
00:26:40.830 --> 00:26:41.700
What?!

457
00:26:45.830 --> 00:26:47.840
Shut your damn mouth!

458
00:26:51.380 --> 00:26:53.510
Hey, Ryokugyu!

459
00:26:54.720 --> 00:26:55.930
Ryokugyu!

460
00:26:56.300 --> 00:26:59.890
You imbecile! If even one of us
gets a scratch, we'll have your head!

461
00:26:59.890 --> 00:27:01.890
I can't go all out like this!

462
00:27:01.890 --> 00:27:03.600
Just get out of here already!

463
00:27:09.690 --> 00:27:10.280
Huh?

464
00:27:10.780 --> 00:27:12.280
Hey, Fujitora!

465
00:27:12.280 --> 00:27:13.990
What are you doing?!

466
00:27:14.610 --> 00:27:16.200
I'm bringing down...

467
00:27:16.200 --> 00:27:17.660
a meteor.

468
00:27:17.660 --> 00:27:18.870
You can't do that!

469
00:27:18.870 --> 00:27:19.910
Stop it, you moron!

470
00:27:21.370 --> 00:27:23.450
Two admirals...

471
00:27:23.450 --> 00:27:27.330
If this weren't the Land of the Gods,
they could decimate the entire landscape.

472
00:27:27.330 --> 00:27:29.340
But they're still causing a scene.

473
00:27:30.920 --> 00:27:34.970
The Revolutionary Army is putting up
a good fight, despite their disadvantage.

474
00:27:35.430 --> 00:27:39.720
Their commanders must be quite strong...

475
00:27:39.720 --> 00:27:40.890
How intense!

476
00:27:42.220 --> 00:27:43.310
Well...

477
00:27:43.770 --> 00:27:47.400
I suppose we should get going as well.

478
00:28:00.280 --> 00:28:01.080
Sabo.

479
00:28:01.530 --> 00:28:03.330
Have you found the collar keys?

480
00:28:03.330 --> 00:28:05.040
It won't take much longer.

481
00:28:05.620 --> 00:28:07.330
I just found out where they are.

482
00:28:08.790 --> 00:28:10.040
Lindbergh!

483
00:28:10.040 --> 00:28:11.340
What is it?

484
00:28:11.710 --> 00:28:13.840
Kuma is now at Pangaea Castle!

485
00:28:13.840 --> 00:28:14.550
What?!

486
00:28:16.260 --> 00:28:19.300
I saw Saint Rosward and his son Charlos...

487
00:28:19.890 --> 00:28:22.760
<b>Chief of Staff Sabo
Revolutionary Army</b>

488
00:28:23.140 --> 00:28:26.940
I think they're headed to Unity Courtyard
to finish what they started...

489
00:28:26.940 --> 00:28:28.900
What?!

490
00:28:30.770 --> 00:28:34.320
I'll make her my pet this time for sure.

491
00:28:34.690 --> 00:28:36.900
He hasn't given up on Princess Shirahoshi...

492
00:28:37.280 --> 00:28:39.860
We can't let them use Kuma for that!

493
00:28:40.200 --> 00:28:43.330
Don't worry, I won't let them do anything!

494
00:28:43.330 --> 00:28:45.660
Morley... get ready!

495
00:28:45.660 --> 00:28:46.750
Okay!

496
00:28:47.250 --> 00:28:50.710
I'll rescue Kuma... no matter what!

497
00:28:54.840 --> 00:28:56.090
Dad!

498
00:29:09.980 --> 00:29:11.730
Please go back to your room.

499
00:29:11.730 --> 00:29:13.060
Will you leave me alone?!

500
00:29:13.560 --> 00:29:16.150
I'm going to Vice Admiral Garp for help!

501
00:29:16.730 --> 00:29:19.070
We are already here to protect you.

502
00:29:19.070 --> 00:29:24.450
Like how you protected Shirahoshi earlier?

503
00:29:24.780 --> 00:29:26.490
You're not stupid!

504
00:29:26.490 --> 00:29:29.960
You know they'll go after her again!

505
00:29:35.210 --> 00:29:37.960
Chaka, Pell.

506
00:29:37.960 --> 00:29:41.590
This is my chance
to finally meet the Five Elders.

507
00:29:41.590 --> 00:29:45.600
I may never have
an opportunity like this again.

508
00:29:49.560 --> 00:29:51.140
Halt!

509
00:29:51.140 --> 00:29:54.520
Only King Cobra is permitted
an audience with the Five Elders.

510
00:29:54.520 --> 00:29:55.570
But...

511
00:29:55.570 --> 00:29:57.280
Stand back.

512
00:29:58.860 --> 00:30:03.990
This shouldn't take long, but don't
bore yourselves waiting around for me.

513
00:30:03.990 --> 00:30:06.330
Go and guard over Vivi instead.

514
00:30:06.330 --> 00:30:08.910
That girl is still so mischievous.

515
00:30:08.910 --> 00:30:11.330
She's always making me worry!

516
00:30:18.410 --> 00:30:23.500
Running so long lost track of just how long its been

517
00:30:24.350 --> 00:30:30.860
Collected scars while striving not even trying beneath my skin

518
00:30:31.360 --> 00:30:38.280
But in the back of my head the dream is not dead I remember a map

519
00:30:38.360 --> 00:30:44.570
to a treasure still gleaming its within our grasp

520
00:30:44.710 --> 00:30:51.480
Can you feel my heart Feelings I impart

521
00:30:51.440 --> 00:30:58.590
The promises are there theyre deep down but still primed to share

522
00:30:58.720 --> 00:31:07.700
Peerless dreams kept close the dreams that always matter most

523
00:31:07.880 --> 00:31:13.450
Before we set sail why not raise a toast

524
00:31:13.570 --> 00:31:20.480
So I pen this note to you Dear sunrise Ill see you soon

525
00:31:20.640 --> 00:31:27.670
See the smile I saw the day that I sang this song to you

526
00:31:27.650 --> 00:31:34.720
And regardless of our age these memries will still remain

527
00:31:34.620 --> 00:31:41.830
Wont forget until this wish makes it to you
